skills/security/wiki-instruction-guard/references/domain-allowlist-local.md
# Local-only IP patterns for pre-commit/pre-push scanning
.ip-patterns
.ip-check-patterns
__pycache__/
install-state/
# Internal planning, design, and operational docs — not for public repo
docs/superpowers/plans/
docs/superpowers/specs/
docs/superpowers/multi-agent/
# Internal operational tooling — not for public repo
tools/internal-sync.sh
# Local AI agent guidance — .ai-guidance/invariants.md IS tracked (repo-wide rules)
